query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_attractions, 
       SUM(CASE WHEN heroImage IS NOT NULL AND heroImage != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_images,
       SUM(CASE WHEN heroImage IS NULL OR heroImage = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_images
FROM attraction_guides;
